sub_title: Research fellow at the National University of Singapore
summary: His research interest lies in the thermal, chemical, and optical sciences in the field of energy engineering. The current research is related to modeling transport phenomena of multi-phase flow in the design of a high-temperature particle solar reactor.

projects:
[{'title': 'Portable Integrated Gasifier & Fuel Cell for Power & Clean Water Generation', 'date': {'start': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2013}}, 'description': 'A 5 kW clean energy generator and water purifier is designed that can serve 4 houses in rural parts of India.

The system converts cow dung and saw-dust briquettes into producer gas, that is fed through palladium-copper (Pd-Cu) membrane for hydrogen separation. Hydrogen is then fed into the anode of a Fuel Cell stack to produce electricity. A portion of this electricity is intended to run the pump needed for feeding contaminated water into an Ultra-filtration unit to produce clean water.

14 kg/h feed stock which contains 3.6 kg/h of cow dung (25%) and 10.64 kg/h of sawdust (75%) is needed and that is equivalent to 9-11 cows for one full-day operation. All the components are sized to serve the required capacity.', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Bo', 'last_name': 'Wang', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Research fellow at the National University of Singapore'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Farid', 'last_name': 'Ellakany', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Account Manager International Rental'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Sriram', 'last_name': 'Krishnamurthy', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Sustainability Consultant | LEED, CEA, GRI Certified Sustainability Professional'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Ajimufti', 'last_name': 'Azhari', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Business Development Manager, Renewables Platform'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Sushant', 'last_name': 'Madaan', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Sustainability I Aquaponics I Erasmus Mundus'}]}]
